ygData.subject: what to kill at 22?? Tib and Rathe Mountains??
ygData.msgSnippet: Tib is in the Rathe Mountains?   Where at?   What lvl is he/she??? Also I would love to hear where I can find some MOBs that are L22-L25 I would love to find
ygData.messageBody:
Tib is in the Rathe Mountains? Where at? What lvl is he/she???

Also I would love to hear where I can find some MOBs that are L22-L25

LMK I have been 22 forever. :-( Thanks!
